Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:20.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:31.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:41.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何处寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前这冷酷无情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理无从寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:57.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}仅有肮脏的抢与夺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一场派对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命运纵横交错的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向着终点一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论胜者或败者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或许某物已然疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑问为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:20.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切尽皆消失在这片虚无之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}现在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:31.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高举这份决心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}来吧  继续BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:41.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束缚  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我们只需变得疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需变得疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦或地狱  GO CRY GO
